data.description: WELCOME HOME! Your 4 bd/2.5 bth 2653 sq ft home awaits! Walk into laminate floors & open concept living on the main floor. Chef's kitchen w/ granite countertops, stainless steel appliances & oversized pantry for all your culinary desires. Second level hosts all 4 bedrooms w/ 2 full bathrooms & bonus space that can be used as an office. Third level is your oversized loft/bonus room/guest space with full size closet. The oversized 3 car garage has plenty of parking, as well as overhead storage that stays. Easy maintenance backyard that can be converted into one big patio space for entertaining. Forced air w/ A/C unit already installed. This home has it all! FHA Assumable at 2.875%!
